question: Which stock indexes should investors invest in? Analyze NASDAQ, S&P 500, Dow Jones performances
query: SELECT    stock_index,    AVG(close_price) AS avg_close_price,    AVG(daily_high) AS avg_daily_high,    AVG(daily_low) AS avg_daily_low FROM    finance_economics_dataset WHERE    stock_index IN ('NASDAQ', 'S&P 500', 'Dow Jones') GROUP BY    stock_index ORDER BY    avg_close_price DESC LIMIT 50;
